INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2014-04-22 02:50:18','2014-04-22 02:50:18','<div id=\"mission-block-container\"><div id=\"text-top\"><h1>welcome to <br/><i>ocean wonders: sharks!</i></h1><h2>An exciting transformation is about to happen</h2><h3>Scroll down to learn more</h3><div id=\"arrow-down\"><a href=\"arrow-down\"></a></div></div><div id=\"text-bottom\"><h2>Right now, friends from around the world are helping us build the <i>new</i> New York Aquarium</h2></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"accordion\">\r\n  <h3>General questions</h3>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>WHAT IS THIS WEBSITE FOR?</h2>\r\nThis website was created to generate support for the Campaign for the New York Aquarium.\r\n<h2>HOW EXACTLY WILL THE MONEY BE USED?</h2>\r\nProceeds from the Campaign will fund the new <em>Ocean Wonders: Sharks!</em> building at the New York Aquarium, as well as an expansion of the Aquarium’s collection of aquatic wildlife, upgrades to animal care, and needed improvements to infrastructure.\r\n<h2>CAN I DONATE A REAL SHIMMER WALL TILE?</h2>\r\nOnly digital tiles are offered as part of the Campaign for the New York Aquarium.  Your recognition may be only virtual, but the support you can provide is real!\r\n  </div>\r\n  <h3>Billing and privacy</h3>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>CAN I BE SURE ALL SENSITIVE DATA IS SECURE?</h2>\r\nYes. Your credit card information will only be stored by Convio, our fully licensed and PCI-compliant payment partner. Click <a style=\"color:#FFF454;text-decoration:underline !important;\" href=\"http://www.convio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> to learn more about Convio’s policies and practices.\r\n<h2>IS MY DONATION TAX DEDUCTIBLE?</h2>\r\nYes! All donations are in support of the Wildlife Conservation Society’s New York Aquarium, a 501(c)(3) charitable organization.\r\n  </div>\r\n  <h3>Making a donation</h3>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>CAN I BE SURE ALL SENSITIVE DATA IS SECURE?</h2>\r\nYes. Your credit card information will only be stored by Convio, our fully licensed and PCI-compliant payment partner. Click <a style=\"color:#FFF454;text-decoration:underline !important;\" href=\"http://www.convio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> to learn more about Convio’s policies and practices.\r\n<h2>IS MY DONATION TAX DEDUCTIBLE?</h2>\r\nYes! All donations are in support of the Wildlife Conservation Society’s New York Aquarium, a 501(c)(3) charitable organization.\r\n  </div>\r\n  <h3>Other questions</h3>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>WHO DESIGNED OCEAN WONDERS: SHARKS!?</h2>\r\nThe building and the exhibit have been designed in a collaborative effort between the Wildlife Conservation Society’s Design Department, The Portico Group and their consultant team including Doyle Partners, and the artist of the shimmer wall, Ned Kahn. The Architect of Record is the New York based firm, Edelman Sultan Knox Wood.\r\n<h2>WHERE CAN I FIND ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ABOUT THIS PROJECT?</h2>\r\nFurther information about the Campaign for the New York Aquarium can be found at <a style=\"color:#FFF454;text-decoration:underline !important;\" href=\"http://www.nyaquarium.com/transform\" target=\"_blank\">www.nyaquarium.com/transform</a>.\r\n<h2>WHERE CAN I REPORT OFFENSIVE CONTENT?</h2>\r\nWe endeavor to monitor all the content that appears on this site. If you believe you have found objectionable content, please email <a style=\"color:#FFF454;text-decoration:underline !important;\" href=\"mailto:nyashimmerwall@wcs.org\">nyashimmerwall@wcs.org</a>.\r\n<h2>MY PROBLEM IS NOT LISTED IN THE FAQ. WHO CAN I CONTACT FOR HELP?</h2>\r\nPlease contact <a style=\"color:#FFF454;text-decoration:underline !important;\" href=\"mailto:nyashimmerwall@wcs.org\">nyashimmerwall@wcs.org</a> and be assured you will receive a prompt response.\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>','Our Mission','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-05-31 20:01:50','2014-05-31 20:01:50','',0,'http://ny3.dev/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(9,1,'2014-05-31 19:12:45','2014-05-31 19:12:45','<div id=\"mission-block-cont